{"tid":1317194,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"轉載【立場新聞】無綫新聞兩採訪車遭破壞　玻璃被打碎　台徽遭噴黑","createTime":"2019-07-14T17:45:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T18:18:23.000Z","uid":65738,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"69b6ead42cf7fd443c178be1adc12df52fb17e95","tid":1317194,"uid":65738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:45:28.000Z","msg":"無綫電視有攝影師及記者採訪今日下午的沙田反修例遊行時遇襲後，兩部新聞車晩上遭人破壞，採訪隊當時採訪示威者在沙田的活動，一部新聞車停在城門河另一邊，車頭玻璃和車尾玻璃被人打破。而另一部新聞車車頭前的台徽被人噴黑油。<br />\n<br />\n無綫電視攝影師及記者採訪今日下午的沙田反修例遊行時，被數人襲擊。無綫電視新聞部發聲明，「嚴厲譴責暴徒」，已報警處理，促警方「緝拿暴徒歸案」。<br />\n<br />\n記協發聲指出，據了解無綫新聞記者和攝影師在執行正常採訪任務期間，先被指罵後，懷疑被示威者踢腳拳打，記者試圖追究時被其他在場示威者箍頸，記協譴責這些暴力行為，並要求有關人士停止對記者的暴力行為。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/tvb-15_5BZMG_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ftvb-15_5BZMG_1200x0.png&h=a64d0cd5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c6e224e216052e8cc65e984f302f871aa0512f0","tid":1317194,"uid":65738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:45:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E7%84%A1%E7%B6%AB%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%85%A9%E6%8E%A1%E8%A8%AA%E8%BB%8A%E9%81%AD%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E-%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%93%E7%A2%8E-%E5%8F%B0%E5%BE%BD%E9%81%AD%E5%99%B4%E9%BB%91/?fbclid=IwAR0sIW96p2pbKPPvrRPQuDzRd21SMDfNj0h7wmdFUmJKZ8O-vw62TFo46ag#.XStmRHX-B6I.facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B6%25AB%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%258E%25A1%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E5%25A3%259E-%25E7%258E%25BB%25E7%2592%2583%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2589%2593%25E7%25A2%258E-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%25BE%25BD%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%2599%25B4%25E9%25BB%2591%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0sIW96p2pbKPPvrRPQuDzRd21SMDfNj0h7w